{"tid":1267670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到 古代攻城 一定要有梯","createTime":"2019-06-30T04:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:40:13.000Z","uid":109780,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4bc96d64216d2dc35afdd280693ef536c137b0","tid":1267670,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"發夢見到古代攻城掠地<br />\n一定會有梯，而且一定有戰車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PkO03Cg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPkO03Cg.jpg&h=4fe7d67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下純粹學術交流 比較現代與古代的科技<br />\n如果對方城牆岩岩好高過一個人<br />\n換做現代而言，係唔係只要有一架車泊係城牆隔離<br />\n就可以比人爬上去入城呢，當然高身既吉普車會更加好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6fyEbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6fyEbY.jpg&h=d2c6def6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，最重要亦最低成本既<br />\n一定係梯啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QreL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QreL8.jpg&h=a1f37b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 本人 熱愛和平 反對戰爭 反對任何違法行為 以上全部都係發夢內容加學術討論"},{"pid":"69a1aba0838abfdb4c7ca8876e67a4ddcca51977","tid":1267670,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎冇人對歷史有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ac36cba69eb69d2c7aefbe365f8f843bb7fcca","tid":1267670,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242f85a5430d00b5c028555a5ec84d5704e67ce5","tid":1267670,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:19:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73e1e3c7265dc1868283f81d725c67175e6f03fa","tid":1267670,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea4d9893c05dbb3572381f96b78c051018779793","tid":1267670,"uid"